Available Tools: create_deal | update_deal_stage | get_deal | list_deals_by_stage | close_deal
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "deal_id": "string", "contact_id": "string", "stage": "string", "value": number }
Response Schema: { "deal_id": "string", "name": "string", "stage": "string", "value": number, "probability": number }
---
Question: Establish a new deal for Globex Corporation with contact ID C-7701 in the prospect stage valued at 22000.
Call: { "func_call": "create_deal", "deal_id": "D-3001", "contact_id": "C-7701", "stage": "prospect", "value": 22000 }
Response: { "deal_id": "D-3001", "name": "Globex Marketing Push", "stage": "prospect", "value": 22000, "probability": 10 }

